longBusinessSummary: Loyal Solutions A/S engages in the development, implementation, and operation of SaaS loyalty solutions worldwide. The company offers LoyalTfacts, a SaaS end-to-end platform. It provides solutions for loyalty, financial, airlines, malls, hospitality, telecom, security, and technology industries. Loyal Solutions A/S was incorporated in 2005 and is headquartered in Copenhagen, Denmark.
